case.title: West coast seeks East coast - 43
case.text: Hi SWF in California. Headed to NYC in a few for work. Work for a large bank as a mortgage banker. Maybe u could show me around! I love sports (football, baseball , tennis) cooking, reading, movies, etc. I have 2 kiddos- so having that in common is great! Lets chat!! I have pix, but cannot upload to CL.
